      <title>Hexo+github搭建个人博客（一）将Hexo部署到GitHub并实现发布文章</title>
      <link href="/2023/04/29/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4/"/>
      <url>/2023/04/29/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="网站教程"><a href="#网站教程" class="headerlink" title="网站教程"></a>网站教程</h1><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/mjh1667002013/article/details/129290903?spm=1001.2014.3001.5506">https://blog.csdn.net/mjh1667002013/article/details/129290903?spm=1001.2014.3001.5506</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_58608526/article/details/124652412?spm=1001.2014.3001.5506">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_58608526&#x2F;article&#x2F;details&#x2F;124652412?spm&#x3D;1001.2014.3001.5506</a><br>完整：<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/">https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/</a></p><h1 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title="安装Git"></a>安装Git</h1><h1 id="安装nodejs"><a href="#安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="安装nodejs"></a>安装nodejs</h1><p>Hexo是基于node.js编写的，所以需要安装一下node.js和里面的npm工具。<br>下载稳定版或者最新版都可以Node.js，安装选项全部默认，一路点击Next。<br>最后安装好之后，按Win+R打开命令提示符，输入node -v和npm -v，如果出现版本号，那么就安装成功了。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682854430685-7fb30a94-01c0-48cf-9a76-e76eac25a082.png#averageHue=%23121110&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=124&id=u95ab369d&originHeight=204&originWidth=343&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=9120&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud9904e6e-fcf3-4141-81e4-b0c0f46e3af&title=&width=207.8787758637182" alt="image.png"><br><img src="/2023-05-01-10-19-51.png"></p><h1 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h1><p>前面git和nodejs安装好后，就可以安装hexo了，你可以先创建一个文件夹<strong>MyBlog</strong>，用来存放自己的博客文件，然后cd到这个文件夹下（或者在这个文件夹下直接右键git bash打开）。<br>比如我的博客文件都存放在D:\Study\MyBlog目录下。<br>在该目录下右键点击Git Bash Here，打开git的控制台窗口，以后我们所有的操作都在git控制台进行，就不用Windows自带的cmd了。<br> 定位到该目录下，输入npm install -g hexo-cli安装Hexo。可能会有几个报错，无视它就行。  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完后输入<code>hexo -v</code>验证是否安装成功。<br>至此hexo就安装完了。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682855659482-ff3bdfd6-1c45-414f-a332-929078e94807.png#averageHue=%23040302&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=408&id=u009cdfae&originHeight=674&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1836989&status=done&style=none&taskId=u72f6b5a2-5965-4b66-817d-3cbc31412bb&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br>接下来初始化一下hexo,即初始化我们的网站，进入我们主题根目录Hexo，输入hexo init初始化文件夹</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">hexo init<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682855666290-c68e296b-c970-46ea-bf2d-b916dc729065.png#averageHue=%23090806&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=61&id=ufaca00ba&originHeight=100&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=272620&status=done&style=none&taskId=u49fab265-0c1f-4c75-8bcc-259c652f4be&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br>这个Hexo可以自己取什么名字都行，然后，接着输入<code>npm install</code>安装必备的组件。  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682856563562-efcb8d98-be71-4906-a217-0187cf362f5e.png#averageHue=%23020201&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=93&id=u9d8a02ec&originHeight=154&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=419790&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud599a164-b2fd-4132-944a-45586f58f48&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br>新建完成后，指定文件夹MyBlog目录下有：</p><ul><li>node_modules: 依赖包</li><li>public：存放生成的页面</li><li>scaffolds：生成文章的一些模板</li><li>source：用来存放你的文章</li><li>themes：主题**</li><li>_config.yml: 博客的配置文件**</li></ul><p> 这样本地的网站配置也弄好啦，输入hexo g生成静态网页，然后输入hexo s打开本地服务器<br> 按ctrl+c关闭本地服务器。  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">hexo <span class="hljs-title function_">g</span> <span class="hljs-params">(hexo generate)</span><br>hexo <span class="hljs-title function_">server</span><span class="hljs-params">(或者简写:hexo s）)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682856605106-cc331662-2ea3-40be-a8fd-c30c23298b09.png#averageHue=%23050403&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=294&id=u0f4ceeee&originHeight=485&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1321901&status=done&style=none&taskId=ub12c9df6-bd43-4a89-8a47-8f633c7bbfa&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682856576098-8946095f-a3ed-4b9d-b05e-250957fbfe2d.png#averageHue=%23918f87&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=353&id=u0231ab79&originHeight=583&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1588983&status=done&style=none&taskId=ub6ae8d71-90a1-4a9c-a2f7-43d94d8f6b6&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"></p><h1 id="注册Github账号创建个人仓库"><a href="#注册Github账号创建个人仓库" class="headerlink" title="注册Github账号创建个人仓库"></a>注册Github账号创建个人仓库</h1><p>接下来就去注册一个github账号，用来存放我们的网站。大多数小伙伴应该都有了吧，作为一个合格的程序猿（媛）还是要有一个的。<br>打开<a href="https://github.com/%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93New">https://github.com/，新建一个项目仓库New</a> repository，如下所示：<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857003330-29e27c33-bd4b-4c33-abef-bf46171d9f29.png#averageHue=%230c1016&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=495&id=uecf54f5a&originHeight=817&originWidth=778&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=68247&status=done&style=none&taskId=u7c6988c2-f6a4-4ba0-a5dc-d85448cafe5&title=&width=471.5151242623113" alt="image.png"><br>要创建一个和你用户名相同的仓库，只有这样，将来要部署到GitHub page的时候，才会被识别。<br>输入格式为：用户名.github.io</p><h1 id="生成SSH添加到GitHub"><a href="#生成SSH添加到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="生成SSH添加到GitHub"></a>生成SSH添加到GitHub</h1><p>生成SSH添加到GitHub，连接Github与本地。<br>在MyBlog中右键打开git bash， 第一次使用git后需要将用户名和邮箱进行初始化 ，输入下面命令：  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;yourname&quot;</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;youremail&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857405866-555fcb4f-5d7d-4762-863b-dfc09db56494.png#averageHue=%2312110f&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=81&id=u7f1423c4&originHeight=133&originWidth=651&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=347108&status=done&style=none&taskId=u30edb6ec-542d-4e5b-af60-25bd7bc85d9&title=&width=394.5454317413427" alt="image.png"><br>这里的yourname输入你的GitHub用户名，youremail输入你GitHub的邮箱。这样GitHub才能知道你是不是对应它的账户。例如我的：  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;gaiolan&quot;</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2942892675@qq.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 可以用以下两条，检查一下你有没有输对  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">git config user.name<br>git config user.email<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>ssh，简单来讲，就是一个秘钥，其中，id_rsa是你这台电脑的私人秘钥，不能给别人看的，id_rsa.pub是公共秘钥，可以随便给别人看。把这个公钥放在GitHub上，这样当你链接GitHub自己的账户时，它就会根据公钥匹配你的私钥，当能够相互匹配时，才能够顺利的通过git上传你的文件到GitHub上。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;youremail&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建SSH，输入命令后，一路回车<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857478548-727d419f-a372-447c-97fa-84c9b5ce7974.png#averageHue=%231c1b1a&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=244&id=uc087e8fe&originHeight=403&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1098408&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud3c21115-5f01-4f15-b510-4fd0415ce11&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br> 这个时候它会告诉你已经生成了.ssh的文件夹。在你的电脑中找到这个文件夹。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857548278-99b65b28-0918-4cf3-ba0f-a5a751ad4c0a.png#averageHue=%232a2929&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=247&id=u59786c02&originHeight=407&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1109316&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud8bd96e9-7c21-4481-ac44-3cd9784fb34&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br> 打开<a href="http://github.com/">github</a>，在头像下面点击settings，再点击SSH and GPG keys，新建一个SSH，名字随便取一个都可以，把你的id_rsa.pub里面的信息复制进去。如图：<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857605834-594d6412-c359-4c28-a46f-6df9744a1ed1.png#averageHue=%230d1116&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=188&id=u3ad54ee6&originHeight=311&originWidth=679&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=846432&status=done&style=none&taskId=u583936ad-9d44-4e98-9b55-dd7dc2653cd&title=&width=411.51512773021767" alt="image.png"><br> 在git bash输入<code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>，如果如下图所示，出现你的用户名，那就成功了。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857657846-401e4921-8a70-4493-8dcf-9a5d86c75a27.png#averageHue=%230b0a09&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=47&id=u0d34ffe3&originHeight=77&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=209931&status=done&style=none&taskId=u63f085eb-7b05-4a24-839c-e9e4df14ad4&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br>如果失败，参考这篇教程<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40047019/article/details/122898308">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40047019/article/details/122898308</a> </p><h1 id="将Hexo部署到GitHub"><a href="#将Hexo部署到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="将Hexo部署到GitHub"></a>将Hexo部署到GitHub</h1><p>这一步，我们就可以将hexo和GitHub关联起来，也就是将hexo生成的文章部署到GitHub上，打开博客根目录下的_config.yml文件，这是博客的配置文件，在这里你可以修改与博客配置相关的各种信息。<br>修改最后一行的配置：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"># Deployment<br>## Docs: https:<span class="hljs-comment">//hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span><br>deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repository: https:<span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/techniquenotes/techniquenotes.github.io.git</span><br>  branch: main<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>repository修改为你自己的github项目地址即可就是部署时，告诉工具，将生成网页通过git方式上传到你对应的链接仓库中。<br>这个时候需要先安装deploy-git ，也就是部署的命令,这样你才能用命令部署到GitHub。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857903213-5cc79ca8-2b67-47f4-8cfe-af5a79bdb960.png#averageHue=%232a2928&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=302&id=u050000fa&originHeight=499&originWidth=679&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1358052&status=done&style=none&taskId=u10302ee0-4eb6-4893-a3a0-3dbe3d25ff0&title=&width=411.51512773021767" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857916458-f89b6af4-5ccc-4f2c-b72f-ce21267e6e74.png#averageHue=%23fbfaf9&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=390&id=u778184e7&originHeight=644&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1755229&status=done&style=none&taskId=u9b2a74a8-7afc-4cd9-8280-beb8b99fa5e&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br> 这个时候需要先安装deploy-git ，也就是部署的命令,这样你才能用命令部署到GitHub。  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682857927739-35b75951-d155-4568-94bd-440731ea9efd.png#averageHue=%230b0a08&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=125&id=u66d99629&originHeight=207&originWidth=601&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=498714&status=done&style=none&taskId=u7782038f-9936-4c5b-a793-f4880d1a96b&title=&width=364.2424031897803" alt="image.png"><br> 其中 hexo clean清除了你之前生成的东西，也可以不加。 hexo generate顾名思义，生成静态文章，可以用 hexo g缩写 ，hexo deploy部署文章，可以用hexo d缩写  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">hexo clean <span class="hljs-comment">//缩写成 hexo cl</span><br>hexo generate <span class="hljs-comment">// 缩写hexo g</span><br>hexo deploy <span class="hljs-comment">// hexo deploy</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858028721-4523d427-45e5-48a4-85e0-a5b9490712a4.png#averageHue=%23070504&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=104&id=u574a0063&originHeight=172&originWidth=511&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=352383&status=done&style=none&taskId=u68ecb8c9-9cb0-4f6a-a603-50e38fa8b49&title=&width=309.69695179696794" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858037701-c98b25d0-b673-487f-a522-196bf9c48bb4.png#averageHue=%23070504&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=291&id=ufb987194&originHeight=480&originWidth=646&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1242881&status=done&style=none&taskId=uc6b9b3db-2010-43d5-ab08-e222110f5d2&title=&width=391.5151288861865" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858050677-3231df2d-9280-41bb-9111-af6cee30dac9.png#averageHue=%230a0705&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=544&id=u2b1bd17d&originHeight=897&originWidth=645&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=2318975&status=done&style=none&taskId=uf65df427-b50e-495e-845d-884fb68e2bc&title=&width=390.90906831515525" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858119217-34b016ce-ebbf-4a8e-912f-a9bb8e4e7f97.png#averageHue=%230e1419&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=237&id=u10587a73&originHeight=391&originWidth=679&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=1064139&status=done&style=none&taskId=ub8326237-5b58-4b5c-9993-43814717057&title=&width=411.51512773021767" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858126484-deb60a3b-5c1e-4b4a-9e4f-719e86346c4f.png#averageHue=%232c3338&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=219&id=ua79f428d&originHeight=361&originWidth=679&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=982494&status=done&style=none&taskId=u5396a4f1-a04e-43fa-a637-b55ba4732ee&title=&width=411.51512773021767" alt="image.png"></p><h1 id="写文章、发布文章"><a href="#写文章、发布文章" class="headerlink" title="写文章、发布文章"></a>写文章、发布文章</h1><p>首先在博客根目录下右键打开git bash，安装一个扩展<code>npm i hexo-deployer-git</code>。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858298090-a048e35d-9f8b-4d57-b8b8-30d42bb03698.png#averageHue=%230b0907&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=124&id=ued824239&originHeight=205&originWidth=495&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=406842&status=done&style=none&taskId=u6641be9e-268c-4dea-860b-06fd68197f4&title=&width=299.999982660468" alt="image.png"><br>然后输入hexo new post “我的第一篇博客”，新建一篇文章。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858314599-a02aae12-c5c8-4d3e-a03a-25d2104316ee.png#averageHue=%23090706&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=68&id=u7d995de7&originHeight=112&originWidth=664&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=298145&status=done&style=none&taskId=uaaca5f85-1472-424c-a1e2-ce0dc08f798&title=&width=402.424219164749" alt="image.png"><br>然后打开D:\Hexo\source_posts的目录，可以发现下面多了一个文件夹和一个.md文件，一个用来存放你的图片等数据，另一个就是你的文章文件啦。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858349291-43308fd2-312f-4334-b1bc-403e9482c067.png#averageHue=%23242323&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=124&id=u9076319d&originHeight=204&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=556052&status=done&style=none&taskId=ube4c23fa-724e-4303-be2f-29d57e603be&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br>你可以会直接在vscode里面编写markdown文件，可以实时预览，也可以用用其他编辑md文件的软件的工具编写。<br>编写完markdown文件后，根目录下输入hexo g生成静态网页，然后输入hexo s可以本地预览效果，最后输入hexo d上传到github上。这时打开你的github.io主页就能看到发布的文章啦。<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858500760-e9826972-c9a0-479c-868b-31c36d0c892c.png#averageHue=%23282d35&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=190&id=u0a550939&originHeight=314&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=855856&status=done&style=none&taskId=ue39d5a97-d556-4a45-b33b-402227bb349&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858526023-dad06a1c-ac8b-4705-9f87-b1be738c6019.png#averageHue=%23070504&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=158&id=u829483d2&originHeight=261&originWidth=625&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=653888&status=done&style=none&taskId=u7c1d566a-fb1e-40cf-b884-1c44cc1e846&title=&width=378.78785689453025" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858549388-e9effc7d-c2e6-4deb-a56d-d37954976a1d.png#averageHue=%23080706&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=67&id=u54be61db&originHeight=110&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=299871&status=done&style=none&taskId=ue305fdb5-7ac8-4e4e-a5f7-d44c8f69d8f&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/26022030/1682858556051-d1008fc3-6dc2-4582-98bc-59033e5c0422.png#averageHue=%23c5c0b7&clientId=ue19ee08f-499d-4&from=paste&height=207&id=ub2fdad63&originHeight=342&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=932162&status=done&style=none&taskId=ucd965a9c-3ed3-476e-b6e5-4f2f2819341&title=&width=412.12118830124894" alt="image.png"><br>到这儿基本第一部分就完成了，已经完整搭建起一个比较简陋的个人博客了，接下来我们就可以对我们的博客进行个性化定制了。</p>]]></content>
      
      
